# Shepherd's Brain — Coordination Layer

**DO NOT COMMIT:**
- `.coordination/tasks/inbox/*.md` — Per-task coordination state
- `.coordination/heartbeat.json` — Auto-updated every poll cycle
- `.coordination/registry.json` — Agent state (local only)
- `.coordination/signals/*` — Ephemeral wake signals
- `.coordination/__pycache__/` — Python bytecode

**DO COMMIT:**
- `.coordination/README.md` — Schema documentation
- `.coordination/dispatch.py` — Dispatch daemon
- `.coordination/tasks/task-board.md` — Current task board (auto-generated)
- `.coordination/tasks/inbox/README.md` — Inbox instructions
- `rooms/skills/coordination-layer.md` — Coordination skill

---

*These patterns prevent coordination state from conflicting across machines.*